  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the efficacy and confirm the safety of E0302 in
      patients with Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS) by assessing changes in scores of survival
      rate and functional rating scale.
    </textblock>
